flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: Scheduled daily segmentation assessment (or on-demand run) after nightly data refresh completes and promotion calendar updates are ingested.]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawlers + STREAMS - Ingest master and transactional data (SKU, location, sales history, promotions, inventory, capacity).]
