  N2 --> N3{PB: Process Builder (IF/Rules) + CWB Lifecycle (recommendation view) - Evaluate segmentation results against business thresholds and constraints; surface recommendations.}
  N3 -->|Primary| N4[PB: Process Builder (Transaction) + Remote Functions - Execute allocations and writebacks: update S4 (master/ATP), push plans to Kinaxis, create transfers/orders in WMS/TMS via Remote Functions.]
  N4 --> N5[PB: Cortex Monitoring + Process Builder (Rollback Transaction) + UI Screen - Validate downstream acceptance and monitoring; enable rapid rollback if validation fails within window.]
  N5 --> Z1[Outcome: Touchless, repeatable allocation flows that align inventory and production to revenue-driven demand segments, improved forecast stability and service, measurable reduction in stockouts/overstock at segment level, and ability to revert recent allocations within a defined validation window.]
  N3 -->|Segmentation confidence below thresho...| B1[Route SKU-Location to CWB Lifecycle for manual review and override by demand planner.]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Human-in-the-loop decision prevents inappropriate automatic reallocation; retains audit trail.]
  O1 --> End[End]
